---
import LandingPage from '../../layouts/LandingPage.astro';
---
<LandingPage 
  title="Live Vessel Tracking View" 
  description="Get a comprehensive, real-time overview of all port traffic. Track vessels, monitor delays, and manage operations from a single pane of glass."
>
  <div class="feature-block">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h2>Total Situational Awareness</h2>
      <p>Our ultra-responsive 2D live map provides instant visibility into every movement within your port. High-frequency AIS updates mean you see vessels turn, accelerate, and moor without any lag or ghosting.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-image">🗺️</div>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-block reverse">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h2>Deep Vessel Intelligence</h2>
      <p>Click on any vessel to instantly pull up its full profile, including length, draft, destination, ETA, and ownership details powered by the TrustedDocks maritime database.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-image">🚢</div>
  </div>
</LandingPage>
